title: The One With Monét's Number One Fan
description:
Do you love sibling rivalry? Support our podcast by going to our patreon page, there you’ll find exclusive content and have the ability to support our show. https://www.patreon.com/siblingrivalrypodcast This week Bob and Monét are together in the same room for the first time on the podcast. They discuss Aretha Franklin, Monét's number one fan, Pearl's RuPaul controversy, and whats happening with Bob's eyeball.
